            "description": "I litigate on behalf of global gas suppliers and importers in high value gas price reviews under long term gas contracts. This includes several international arbitrations under the ICC Rules with seats in Sweden and Germany, relating to contracts under German and Norwegian law. Claim values generally exceed \u20ac 500 million. In addition, I advise suppliers and importers in the pre-litigation and negotiation phase of a price review. My expertise includes both the legal and economical elements that are relevant in these price reviews.",
