            "description": "From start to finish, I have been advising on, negotiating and drafting a Share Purchase Agreement between Corio and Multi Corporation for the acquisition of both standing assets as well as development projects in Germany, Spain and Portugal. I have also have been involved in devising a complex financing structure in relation to this acquisition. This included the launch of an offering of new ordinary shares at signing, and a loan for retained shares with a related call option. Due to the various jurisdictions involved, I was also responsible for the management of local counsel due diligence and implementation of local transfer requirements.",
